Class Graph

  • java.lang.Object
    • ramsey.Graph
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Graph>

    public class Graph
extends Object
implements Comparable<Graph>, Serializable
    Represents a complete graph with a 2-color coloring Can be used for finding mono-chrmoatic size cliques Has helper methods for adding nodes, and generating graphs
    Author:
    Michael Nekrasov, Roman Kazarin
    See Also:
